# Root build context (used by services/api/Dockerfile). Keep it lean and never
# ship host build artifacts or secrets into the image. Note: every workspace
# member's package.json must remain visible so the dashboard stage's frozen
# install can resolve the workspace, so we exclude artifacts (node_modules,
# dist) rather than whole package directories.
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.venv/
**/__pycache__/
.git/
.github/
**/tests/
**/*.md
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
docs/
**/cloudformation/
